  "body": "**ISSUE 1. [Send] button is not visible during message editing**\r\n**Steps to reproduce:**\r\n1. Go to 1-1 chat\r\n2. Send the message\r\n3. Long tap on it\r\n4. Add some additional text into the editing textbox\r\n5. Try to tap 'send' button\r\n\r\n**Actual result:**\r\n\r\n[Send] button is not visible\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/209150399-d16e00cd-5ffa-4c01-ac58-6527bd1216a9.mp4\r\n\r\n**Expected result:**\r\n[Send] button is visible\r\n\r\n**ENV:** Android devices\r\n\r\n**ISSUE 2. [Only for IOS devices] The initial message is not shown into the input textbox if 'edit message' option is selected**\r\n\r\n**Steps to reproduce:**\r\n1. Create 1-1 chat\r\n2. Send a message\r\n3. Long tap on the message\r\n4. Tap 'edit message'\r\n\r\n**Actual result:**\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/209154631-c8e00d73-aa94-4e8d-b8b1-dcf4aac73f7a.MP4\r\n\r\nThe initial message that intended to be edited is disappeared\r\n**Expected result:**\r\nThe initial text is shown after 'edit message' option is tapped\r\n\r\n\r\n**ISSUE 3: Mark that the message is edited should be shown**\r\n\r\n**Steps to reproduce:**\r\n1. Go to 1-1 chat\r\n2. Send the message\r\n3. Long tap the message -> tap 'edit  message' option\r\n4. Make some changes -> tap 'send' button\r\n\r\n**Actual result:**\r\nThe changed message is not  marked as 'changed'\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected result:**\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/209155661-bb66c875-8840-4530-a614-20cb9e5d49b5.png)\r\n",
